      lang="en" dir="ltr">
        <div class="cta-card__image">
            <img alt="Gates Foundation staff members pose for a photo after the Grand Challenges Annual Meeting 2017 at the Marriott Marquis in Washington D.C. on October 4, 2017." srcset="/-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga1492247_mm524070.jpg?rev=b8880d0f359a4fe083f44e6d34511acc&amp;w=500&amp;hash=B8CF06FF6D73F2E08C2C4E3D4B28806E 1x, /-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga1492247_mm524070.jpg?rev=b8880d0f359a4fe083f44e6d34511acc&amp;w=1000&amp;hash=45216FE01BCD8DB87B968ADDFB5B2E35 2x" />
        </div>
    <div class="cta-card__title">
	    <span>Seattle and Washington, D.C.</span>
    </div>
        <div class="cta-card__description">
            <p>Our staff in the United States works with governments, nongovernmental organizations, universities, industry, and the philanthropic sector to advance the foundation’s global health and development goals and improve education and economic opportunity in the U.S.</p>
        </div>
            <ul class="cta-card__links" aria-label="Seattle and Washington, D.C.">

                <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/seattle-usa" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Seattle office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/seattle-usa">
<span>Learn more about our Seattle office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                            <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/washington-dc-usa" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Washington, D.C., office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/washington-dc-usa">
<span>Learn more about our Washington, D.C., office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                                            </ul>
</div>
<div class="cta-card component   " 
      lang="en" dir="ltr">
        <div class="cta-card__image">
            <img alt="View of the Gates Foundation offices in London, England on April 11, 2015." srcset="/-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga1353291_mk441608.jpg?rev=381f4bec749f4fb1876ac549dec95c07&amp;w=500&amp;hash=C2071B9F35F401A06B972C12714A08F7 1x, /-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga1353291_mk441608.jpg?rev=381f4bec749f4fb1876ac549dec95c07&amp;w=1000&amp;hash=AE2BDBBD8CC17DBBA2DF0A8CF0E34E4B 2x" />
        </div>
    <div class="cta-card__title">
	    <span>London and Berlin</span>
    </div>
        <div class="cta-card__description">
            <p>Our London and Berlin staff work with grantees and partners across Europe, the Middle East, and East Asia to build and sustain donor government commitment to advancing our global health and development goals. These offices are also home to staff who work on specific foundation initiatives in global health, development, and education.</p>
        </div>
            <ul class="cta-card__links" aria-label="London and Berlin">

                <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/london-uk" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our UK office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/london-uk">
<span>Learn more about our UK office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                            <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/berlin-germany" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Germany office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/berlin-germany">
<span>Learn more about our Germany office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                                            </ul>
</div>
<div class="cta-card component   " 
      lang="en" dir="ltr">
        <div class="cta-card__image">
            <img alt="Employees of the Gates Foundation enjoy a reception at the Annual Employee Meeting in Seattle, Washington, on May 9, 2023." srcset="/-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga17112112_mh650679.jpg?rev=02a47f8a616344fc9137abe8f7de0288&amp;w=500&amp;hash=9B817A42FE0A7D7C1903BE114D9C8756 1x, /-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga17112112_mh650679.jpg?rev=02a47f8a616344fc9137abe8f7de0288&amp;w=1000&amp;hash=80959CC5601FBCB3B8A764EF13E711D5 2x" />
        </div>
    <div class="cta-card__title">
	    <span>Delhi</span>
    </div>
        <div class="cta-card__description">
            <p>Our India-based staff work with the Indian government and other partners—including community groups, nonprofits, academic institutions, the private sector, and development organizations—on issues including health care, sanitation, gender equality, agricultural development, and digital financial services. </p>
        </div>
            <ul class="cta-card__links" aria-label="Delhi">

                <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/delhi-india" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our India office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/delhi-india">
<span>Learn more about our India office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                                                        </ul>
</div>
<div class="cta-card component   " 
      lang="en" dir="ltr">
        <div class="cta-card__image">
            <img alt="Employees of the Gates Foundation pose for a photo during CEO of the Gates Foundation, Mark Suzman&#39;s visit to the Foundation&#39;s South Africa office, in Johannesburg, South Africa, on September 19, 2022." srcset="/-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga17003126_gk632721.jpg?rev=a31d93703269426f95068b214224170e&amp;w=500&amp;hash=8ACCA6FD20CADFEC0B3D999F78B023D3 1x, /-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga17003126_gk632721.jpg?rev=a31d93703269426f95068b214224170e&amp;w=1000&amp;hash=D9E85671368A943E3D9CEF8A188E683A 2x" />
        </div>
    <div class="cta-card__title">
	    <span>Addis Ababa, Abuja, Dakar, Johannesburg, and Nairobi</span>
    </div>
        <div class="cta-card__description">
            <p>Our Africa-based employees work with governments, local organizations, and other partners to improve health and economic opportunity. We offer funding and scientific expertise to support programs spanning health and nutrition, gender equality, disease prevention and treatment, sanitation, agriculture, and financial services.</p>
        </div>
            <ul class="cta-card__links" aria-label="Addis Ababa, Abuja, Dakar, Johannesburg, and Nairobi">

                <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/addis-ababa-ethiopia" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Ethiopia office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/addis-ababa-ethiopia">
<span>Learn more about our Ethiopia office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                            <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/nairobi-kenya" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Kenya office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/nairobi-kenya">
<span>Learn more about our Kenya office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                            <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/abuja-nigeria" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Nigeria office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/abuja-nigeria">
<span>Learn more about our Nigeria office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                            <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/dakar-senegal" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Senegal office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/dakar-senegal">
<span>Learn more about our Senegal office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                            <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/johannesburg-south-africa" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our South Africa office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/johannesburg-south-africa">
<span>Learn more about our South Africa office</span>
</a>
                </li>
        </ul>
</div>
<div class="cta-card component   " 
      lang="en" dir="ltr">
        <div class="cta-card__image">
            <img alt="Mark Suzman poses for a group photo with the Gates Foundation China Country Office team in Beijing, China." srcset="/-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga1458024_sk515528_3x2.jpg?rev=ccede6baf24543cead5b4c220881d4bd&amp;w=500&amp;hash=3C861C0A99FCFA3B0C29C3F5DC1984C6 1x, /-/media/gfo/3about/5careers/ga1458024_sk515528_3x2.jpg?rev=ccede6baf24543cead5b4c220881d4bd&amp;w=1000&amp;hash=D7E27A15AD5ACF1575D8CF793D426785 2x" />
        </div>
    <div class="cta-card__title">
	    <span>Beijing</span>
    </div>
        <div class="cta-card__description">
            <p>Our China-based staff provide financial and technical support to our Chinese partners so they can accelerate product, technology, and systems innovation to improve health, spur agricultural development, and reduce poverty in China and around the world.</p>
        </div>
            <ul class="cta-card__links" aria-label="Beijing">

                <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/beijing-china" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our China office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/beijing-china">
<span>Learn more about our China office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                                                        </ul>
</div>
<div class="cta-card component   " 
      lang="en" dir="ltr">
        <div class="cta-card__image">
            <img alt="Singapore" srcset="/-/media/gfo/3about/4offices/gettyimages-2119892422_3x2.jpg?rev=83d1677866e74da09331dc7655a11580&amp;w=500&amp;hash=AC21E29C4DB216A817EE107233B12301 1x, /-/media/gfo/3about/4offices/gettyimages-2119892422_3x2.jpg?rev=83d1677866e74da09331dc7655a11580&amp;w=1000&amp;hash=4E243F78FCA53A12EE83C61EBD3C30B1 2x" />
        </div>
    <div class="cta-card__title">
	    <span>Singapore</span>
    </div>
        <div class="cta-card__description">
            <p>We opened our Singapore office in 2026 to serve as a regional hub for our work across South and Southeast Asia. From Singapore, we work with governments, regional institutions, and local organizations to help shape and advance efforts that improve health, reduce poverty, and expand opportunity.</p>
        </div>
            <ul class="cta-card__links" aria-label="Singapore">

                <li class="cta-card__link">
                    <a class="arrow-link" data-gtm-element="promo cta" href="/about/offices/singapore" data-gtm-text="Learn more about our Singapore office" data-gtm-link="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/about/offices/singapore">
<span>Learn more about our Singapore office</span>
</a>
                </li>
                                                        </ul>
</div>
    </div>
</section> 
    </div>
</section>

</section>

